item.title: CVE-2023-5111|2024-08-02T07:44:53.816Z -- os%20commerce -- os%20commerce
item.description: Os Commerce is currently susceptible to a Cross-Site Scripting (XSS) vulnerability. This vulnerability allows attackers to inject JS through the "featured_type_name[1]" parameter, potentially leading to unauthorized execution of scripts within a user's web browser.
